1. *Glavu* je podigao iznad vode da bi mogao da diše. (He raised his head above the water so he could breathe.)

2. Ona je stavila svoju *glavu* na moje rameno. (She put her head on my shoulder.)

3. On je izgubio *glavu* kad je čuo tu vest. (He lost his head when he heard that news.)

4. *Glavu* je nagnula napred i zagledala se u zemlju. (She bent her head forward and looked down at the ground.)

5. Oni su okrenuli *glavu* kad su čuli zvuk. (They turned their heads when they heard the sound.)

6. On je pokazao svojim *glavom* u pravcu u kom ide. (He showed with his head in the direction he was going.)